  "texts": [
    "As our main concern is the vehicle camera view, we use the results in this table to rank the models.",
    "It can be seen that using a combination of two or more features is significantly better than just using one of them.",
    "In the experiments where the sub-global feature is directly used in comparison with its global counterpart (row 1 vs row 2 and row 7 vs row 6), the results of both are mostly comparable.",
    "The two best models use the global or sub-global feature alongside the local feature with temporal modelling.",
    "Of the two of them, the one with the sub-global feature (row 7) outperforms its counterpart in 6 out of 8 metrics."
